<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Milira ConceptWeaponry: Cyclops -->
  <Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.label>米莉拉概念兵装：独眼巨人</Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.label>
  <!-- EN: The Milira personal combat weaponry, model Cyclops, has not yet been fully deployed. Equipping with two heavy plasma cannons and four rocket pods, excelling in long-range bombardment. Its integrated Arc Point Defense System effectively intercepts incoming projectiles.\n\nOperation requires solar fuel. -->
  <Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.description>尚未全面投入运用的米莉拉单人兵装，型号为独眼巨人。装备有两门重型离子炮与四个联装火箭巢，擅长远距离炮击战；配备的电弧点防御系统能够有效拦截投射物。\n\n使用需要装填日光燃料。</Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.description>
  <!-- EN: Toggle the Arc Point-Defense System. When enabled, it consumes solar fuel to intercept hostile projectiles within a 5-tile radius. Each interception consumes 1 unit of solar fuel. The system will not function if there is insufficient solar fuel. -->
  <Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompPointDefense.gizmoDesc>开启或关闭电弧点防御系统。处于开启状态时，消耗日光燃料拦截半径5格以内的非友方投射物，每次拦截消耗1日光燃料。日光燃料不足时无法进行拦截。</Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompPointDefense.gizmoDesc>
  <!-- EN: Arc Point-Defense -->
  <Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompPointDefense.gizmoLabel>电弧点防御</Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompPointDefense.gizmoLabel>
  <!-- EN: Fuel -->
  <Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompIntegrationWeaponSystem.chargeNoun>燃料</Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompIntegrationWeaponSystem.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompIntegrationWeaponSystem.cooldownGerund>冷却中</Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompIntegrationWeaponSystem.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: Activate or deactivate the weapon system: Cyclops. When activated, it consumes 1 unit of solar fuel every 5 seconds. The operator can use the weapon system's armaments, abilities, and special effects in combat. -->
  <Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompIntegrationWeaponSystem.gizmoDesc>启动或解除兵装：独眼巨人。兵装启动时每5秒消耗1日光燃料，操作者可以使用兵装的武器、技能与特殊效果进行战斗。</Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompIntegrationWeaponSystem.gizmoDesc>
  <!-- EN: Cyclops -->
  <Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompIntegrationWeaponSystem.gizmoLable>独眼巨人</Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompIntegrationWeaponSystem.gizmoLable>
  <!-- EN: Heavy Plasma Cannon 1 -->
  <Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompTurretGun_Custom-0.gizmoLable>重型电浆炮1</Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompTurretGun_Custom-0.gizmoLable>
  <!-- EN: Heavy Plasma Cannon 2 -->
  <Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompTurretGun_Custom-1.gizmoLable>重型电浆炮2</Milira_ConceptWeaponry_Cyclops.comps.CompTurretGun_Custom-1.gizmoLable>
  
  <!-- EN: heavy plasmon -->
  <MiliraBullet_HeavyPlasmaCannon.label>重型电浆炮</MiliraBullet_HeavyPlasmaCannon.label>
  
  <!-- EN: milira heavy plasma cannon -->
  <MiliraTurret_ConceptWeaponry_PlasmaCannon.label>重型电浆炮</MiliraTurret_ConceptWeaponry_PlasmaCannon.label>
  <!-- EN: A heavy plasma cannon installed on Cyclops. -->
  <MiliraTurret_ConceptWeaponry_PlasmaCannon.description>一门安装在独眼巨人上的重型电浆炮。</MiliraTurret_ConceptWeaponry_PlasmaCannon.description>
  <!-- EN: milira heavy plasma cannon -->
  <MiliraTurret_ConceptWeaponry_PlasmaCannon.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>重型电浆炮</MiliraTurret_ConceptWeaponry_PlasmaCannon.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>
  
